TITLE      Total reflection of neutrons from metallic mirrors.
REFERENCE  (J,RSI,33,916,1962)
AUTHOR     (D.Bally,S.Todireanu,S.Ripeanu,M.G.Belloni)
INSTITUTE  (3RUMBUC)
FACILITY   (REAC,3RUMBUC)
INC-SOURCE To obtain a monochromatic beam of neutrons, a calcite
           mono-crystal cut at an angle of 12.degr. was used, the
           reflection occurring from the cleavage planes.
           The wavelength of the reflected neutrons
                                                was 1.161 Angstr.
METHOD     (REFL)     Total reflection from mirrors
DETECTOR   No details given
STATUS     (TABLE) Data from text of reference
HISTORY    (19771115T) Converted from EXFOR 70272
           (20090912A) SD:Updated to new date formats,lower case.
           Cosmetic changes, experimental details and sample
           description were added.
